    "result": {"data":{"strapiPost":{"strapiId":3860,"title":"Growth In Learning ","topic":"Education","slug":"growth-in-learning","coverImage":{"publicURL":"/static/485c42dddedcfb2b11632832802fbdb8/173e44c23e77fca359dba6536d8cc07c.jpg"},"photoCredit":"LISA Academy","date":"2021-11-16","content":"<p>Northwest Arkansas is about to have another school campus on the block after the Arkansas Board of Education gave approval for <a href=\"https://www.lisaacademy.org/?gclid=Cj0KCQiAhMOMBhDhARIsAPVml-GWCQb3RAHwXfl7pyU1vHCJpZSs5nmAmhg_bTYZTLzbhGDkPKlCYh8aAprMEALw_wcB\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">LISA Academy</a> to offer K-12 in Fayetteville.&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>Steps: </strong>LISA Academy is a <a href=\"https://meetings.boardbook.org/Public/Agenda/1133?meeting=502152\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">tuition free</a> public charter school. There are <a href=\"https://meetings.boardbook.org/Public/Agenda/1133?meeting=502152\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">7 locations</a> across Arkansas serving more than 3600 students. The newest campus will open in stages starting in <a href=\"https://meetings.boardbook.org/Public/Agenda/1133?meeting=502152\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">2023 for K-5</a>, and will be complete for the <a href=\"https://meetings.boardbook.org/Public/Agenda/1133?meeting=502152\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">2026-27 school year</a> for high schoolers.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Footprint: </strong>The eventual Fayetteville campus will be just off I-49 at the <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Van+Asche+Dr+%26+S+McGuire+St,+Johnson,+AR+72704/@36.1172979,-94.1783345,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x87c96c3c62eafafd:0x938cca03efd759be!8m2!3d36.1172979!4d-94.1761458\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">intersection of Van Asche and McGuire</a>. The 2 building campus in Fayetteville will be the 3rd LISA location in NWA after the <a href=\"https://lisaspringdale.lisaacademy.org/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Springdale</a> and <a href=\"https://lisaspringdale.lisaacademy.org/apps/pages/index.jsp?uREC_ID=2595714&amp;type=d&amp;pREC_ID=2262918\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Rogers-Bentonville</a> campuses.&nbsp;</li></ul><p>Learn more <a href=\"https://meetings.boardbook.org/Public/Agenda/1133?meeting=502152\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a></p>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"growth-in-learning"}},
